                            <comment id="16185951" author="thn929" created="Fri, 29 Sep 2017 15:06:46 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Looking at &lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/KAFKA-5986&quot; title=&quot;Streams State Restoration never completes when logging is disabled&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;KAFKA-5986&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;KAFKA-5986&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; and the fix for it in &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/3983&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/3983&lt;/a&gt; : this does indeed seem to be a duplicate. I&apos;ll try running through the same scenario with the fix and report back. Thanks!&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="16186424" author="thn929" created="Fri, 29 Sep 2017 21:08:14 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The fix provided by &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/3983&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://github.com/apache/kafka/pull/3983&lt;/a&gt; did the trick in resolving the initialization/restoration loop, but we&apos;re not at the finish line yet. Working off of trunk, I&apos;ve attached the updated &lt;span class=&quot;nobr&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/attachment/12889770/12889770_App2.java&quot; title=&quot;App2.java attached to KAFKA-5989&quot;&gt;App2.java&lt;sup&gt;&lt;img class=&quot;rendericon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/link_attachment_7.gif&quot; height=&quot;7&quot; width=&quot;7&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/span&gt; to demonstrate the problem.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Basically:&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;loggingEnabled&lt;/tt&gt;: Records are written to the state store as expected.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;tt&gt;loggingDisabled&lt;/tt&gt;: Records do not get written to the state store &lt;img class=&quot;emoticon&quot; src=&quot;https://issues.apache.org/jira/images/icons/emoticons/sad.png&quot; height=&quot;16&quot; width=&quot;16&quot; align=&quot;absmiddle&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; border=&quot;0&quot;/&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;There seems to still be a dependency on changelogs somewhere, but I haven&apos;t found it yet.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
